									</div>
									<div class="profile-content">
										<div class="profile-header">
											<h3>Innocent Nyalala</h3>
											<p class="profile-title">Assistant Professor & Founding Principal Investigator</p>
											<p class="profile-department">School of Engineering and Sciences<br>IIT Madras Zanzibar</p>
